=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describes configuration settings related to outbound network traffic of
an App Runner service.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 EgressType => Str

The type of egress configuration.

Set to C<DEFAULT> for access to resources hosted on public networks.

Set to C<VPC> to associate your service to a custom VPC specified by
C<VpcConnectorArn>.


=head2 VpcConnectorArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the App Runner VPC connector that you
want to associate with your App Runner service. Only valid when
C<EgressType = VPC>.



